text: Cooper's Creek or Coopers Creek may refer to: * Cooper Creek, formerly Cooper's Creek, a river in Queensland and South Australia, Australia *Coopers Creek (New South Wales), a river in Australia *Coopers Creek, New Zealand, a town in the Waimakariri District *Coopers Creek (West Virginia), a stream in the United States *Coopers Creek, Victoria, a former township in Australia *Upstream Cooper River (New Jersey), in the United States
title: Coopers Creek
